From a4e5681d60170dc709a33e5ef7509843ef7a5ee0 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: coherent-cache <rbkv2.0@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 8 Mar 2026 23:46:14 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 1/5] fix: resolve API failures and crash bugs

- Add missing Content-Type: application/json header to API requests,
  which caused 422 errors on all POST endpoints (login, OTP, refresh)
- Update transactions endpoint from v1 to v2 (v1 now returns 404)
- Add bounds checks in transaction pagination to prevent panics on
  empty responses and nil pointer dereferences
- Handle missing ledger file gracefully in parser instead of crashing
- Add --phone and --otp flags to login command for non-interactive use

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
