From 645300881267343a9069207d5f4a338a606ce77e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: coherent-cache <rbkv2.0@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 10 Mar 2026 02:19:46 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 2/5] Preserve enriched transaction metadata from v2 API

The v2 transactions API returns Category, Tags, Mode, Reference, Notes,
and ExcludedFromCashFlow but filterTransactions() was discarding them.
Extend FilteredTransactions struct, db.Transactions model, and writeToDb()
to capture all 6 fields. Enables downstream tools to use Fold's own
classification data (37 categories, payment modes, cash flow exclusions).

