Subject: [PATCH 3/5] Capture enriched v2 API metadata: narration, F1
 predictions, refunds, contacts, groups

Extend FilteredTransactions, db.Transactions, and writeToDb() to preserve
11 additional fields from the Fold v2 API that were previously discarded:

- narration: raw bank narration (3,832/3,833 populated, critical for dedup)
- category_id: stable UUID for Fold categories (38 unique)
- summary: human-readable transaction summary
- transaction_id: Fold's internal txn ID
- is_f1_predicted: whether category/merchant were AI-predicted vs user-set
- refund_status: IS_REFUNDABLE/REFUNDED/STOP_TRACKING (241 txns)
- refund_received_on: timestamp for confirmed refunds (76 txns)
- contact_id: Fold's counterparty linking (45 txns, 19 contacts)
- group_ids: transaction grouping (23 txns in 2 groups)
- account_id: Fold's internal account UUID

Also adds personal financial data files (fold_raw_all.json, local.ledger,
*.sqlite.bak) to .gitignore to prevent accidental exposure.

