Subject: [PATCH 5/5] Capture remaining Fold API fields: merchant_address,
 kind, bookmarks, via
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Store all available Fold v2 API transaction fields locally for future
analysis. Adds merchant_address (physical location, sparse), kind
(transaction type), is_bookmarked, before_fold_account (pre-Fold
historical flag), via (payment intermediary), and account_in.

Schema now captures 31 columns — all non-visual API fields preserved.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
